<h4>It's Time to Register for IAAI-09!</h4>
<p>It's time to plan your trip IAAI-09 in Pasadena. <a href="https://www.aaai.org/Forms/ijcai-registration-form.php">Register</a> and <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/IAAI/2009/iaai09hotels.php">Book your Hotel Room</a> Now! <a href="https://www.aaai.org/Forms/ijcai-registration-form.php"> More&#8230;</a></p>

<h4>Schedule Your Days at IAAI!</h4>
<p>The preliminary schedule for IAAI is now available. <a href="http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/IAAI/2009/iaai09schedule.php"> More&#8230;</a></p>
